      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and has been pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
