    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 3.2L inline-six is a masterpiece, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS system that has been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing. This example features a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox delivering power through a variable M-Differential Lock. The chassis integrity is unparalleled, with the rear subframe reinforced to maintain factory-spec torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black over a flawless Nappa leather interior, the vehicle retains its original suspension geometry and forged Style 67 wheels. A collector-grade specimen with comprehensive service documentation and zero mechanical deficiencies.",
