      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner and kept in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior is in showroom condition, protected by a full-body ceramic coating with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the Black Dakota leather with blue stitching still carries that new-car aroma; the seat bolsters show no signs of wear, and the carbon fiber trim is pristine. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers. It has never seen a track, has never been driven in the rain, and features a completely stock powertrain. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning buyer who demands perfection. All original keys, manuals, and service receipts are included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
