      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive masterclass in naturally aspirated engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for a linear, high-revving power delivery. This example features the coveted 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox, providing tactile mechanical feedback through every gate. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, including a proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul to ensure thermal efficiency. Suspension kinematics remain factory-tight, working in harmony with the M Variable Differential Lock for peerless corner-exit traction. With original paint depth and a pristine cabin, this is a concours-level vehicle for the collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
